headline: UnitedHealth: Bernstein lists 3 top priorities for the new CEO
summary: Investing.com -- In a note to clients on Wednesday, Bernstein identified three critical priorities for UnitedHealth’s new CEO, Steve Hemsley, following the company’s annual shareholder meeting, with pricing discipline emerging as the most immediate focus.
